description:
This is a 12 minute workout called '10MIN full body hourglass pilates workout // no equipment & beginner friendly | LIDIAVMERA' from the channel Lidia Mera.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: perfect for those mornings you don't have much time but still want to get some movement in or for a little night-time pilates session! 

Hope you have fun doing this workout! 
Love you all, Lidi x
